		<title>Mayo Clinic Transplant performs record 2,065 organ transplants in 2025</title>
		<link>https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/mayo-clinic-transplant-performs-record-2065-organ-transplants-in-2025/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Kelley Luckstein]]></dc:creator>
