		<title>New heart helps Loren Vinal return to music, life he loves</title>
		<link>https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/new-heart-helps-loren-vinal-return-to-music-life-he-loves/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[rebeccabromelkamp]]></dc:creator>
